{"tid":2249711,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"係香港人就唔該抵制奶支鬼滅","createTime":"2020-10-19T13:35:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-22T04:15:33.000Z","uid":182935,"like":10,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"f6bd302f542bdc09dac7b9a17f39cc25de999dc7","tid":2249711,"uid":182935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T13:35:04.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">一套係奶共奶到一紅就衝去上海開cafe</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pkjcQur.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpkjcQur.png&h=22b2e32f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">一套係反共反到被上海電影節下架</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7PLzjoe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7PLzjoe.jpg&h=66dfe9c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔使諗到時一定有人拎白箱票房同鬼滅做比較，以鬼滅紅既程度拋離白箱幾個零唔係問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n到時班離地藍絲一定會沾沾自喜，恥笑白箱係小眾玩意動物台毒撚先會睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我地冇面唔緊要，反正平時都俾mk笑到慣晒，但重點係水島努監督幫我地出咗咁多聲，到頭來連套奶共無腦片都比唔上，你地真係咁就甘心咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我喺到呼籲各位同路人同我一齊杯葛鬼滅，入場支持白箱，拒絕沈淪做港豬，stand with 水島努<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d1dc431aa7053af3c0c692759ef0b7ca4f672ca","tid":2249711,"uid":182935,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T13:36:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"233e3cd0070366aa1ad64b43f6b93ccb3e3de4ff","tid":2249711,"uid":106477,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T13:39:12.000Z","msg":"其實日本好多只係賣license <br />\n收咗錢唔撚理做咩<br />\n<br />\nHit個時唔賺幾時賺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e01e6e624a3cfd6853376591ca16f6f58fdb5d14","tid":2249711,"uid":182935,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"233e3cd0070366aa1ad64b43f6b93ccb3e3de4ff","tid":2249711,"uid":106477,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T13:39:12.000Z","msg":"其實日本好多只係賣license <br />\n收咗錢唔撚理做咩<br />\n<br />\nHit個時唔賺幾時賺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T13:40:36.000Z","msg":"日本豬:人民幣呀!!!!!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbe3a0bc3ff09288f52d02abb38016c03dc11175","tid":2249711,"uid":51701,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"233e3cd0070366aa1ad64b43f6b93ccb3e3de4ff","tid":2249711,"uid":106477,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T13:39:12.000Z","msg":"其實日本好多只係賣license <br />\n收咗錢唔撚理做咩<br />\n<br />\nHit個時唔賺幾時賺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T13:45:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tFKcwm9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtFK